<td>District and school name and/or school type (private, public, charter, homeschool, after school, or other) and/or school address</td>
<td>Optional</td>
<td>At the Teacher's option and under their control, we would list their school in the Code.org map and database of schools that teach computer science courses.<br><br>Code.org or our Regional Partners** may also use this information to reach out to the Teacher's school or district to discuss broader education partnerships or participation in special events.</td>
