<td>Forum posts and profiles</td>
<td>Optional</td>
<td>For Teachers who choose to participate in the Teacher support forums at forum.code.org, posts and replies are shared publicly. Teachers may also optionally supply additional information for their forum profile, including their profile picture, location, website, and “about me” text. This information is used in no other way beyond the forum itself.</td>
</tr>
